THE BUTTERFLY - New collab from @adamlisterstudio X Budmen dropping early December.

Made from solid American walnut this limited edition sculpture brings to life the delicately pixelated universe of Adam Lister’s paintings. We have been collaborating  together for over 10 years, in that time we have created 3D printed sculptures, NFTs, movies and more but this is a first for us. THE BUTTERFLY is the first assemble-it-yourself sculpture we have ever created. Challenging and beautifully satisfying. Edition of 150.
How THE BUTTERFLY went from an original @adamlisterstudio watercolor painting to a solid walnut sculpture.

Building The Butterfly. Our first build-it-yourself sculpture with @adamlisterstudio. Made from sustainably harvested American Walnut in an edition of 250. Transformation is a word that defines the life of a butterfly - from caterpillar to chrysalis to magnificent monarch. This sculpture was conceived as a build-it-yourself to capture that transformation as an experience… and as you build from from sheet to sculpture you might just transform yourself… 🦋✨

Available now. Only 250 available. 

A limited edition sculpture that brings an Adam Lister watercolor painting to life in a life-sized form. Made from solid American walnut, this sculpture captures the delicately pixelated universe of Adam Lister’s paintings in a way that has never been done before.

With only 250 available, this is a truly unique and exclusive opportunity to own a one-of-a-kind piece of art. Don’t miss out on your chance to bring THE BUTTERFLY to life.

Link in profile.

The Kick & The Butterfly - two sculptures that represent over 10 years of collaboration between @adamlisterstudio X Budmen. The Kick is made from ceramic polymer and comes in a custom made shoebox, edition of 5. The Butterfly is made from sustainably harvested American Walnut, edition of 250. Available on Budmen.com while supplies last, once they are gone they are gone. Link in profile 👆

👉Out now: The Kick. 👟 A one-of-a-kind sculpture, produced in an extremely limited edition of 5. 

Every detail of this premium piece has been carefully considered and precisely executed, resulting in a true work of art. The luxurious materials and sleek matte finish lend an air of sophistication and tantalizing mystery. 

THE KICK - a uniquely iconic and otherworldly sculpture that beckons you to experience its magic.

Only 5 available. Link in bio 🔗

and Uniqlo. 
I was invited to create artwork that reinterprets some of the most iconic Pixar Animation characters of all time. 
Drawing inspiration from the films “Toy Story”, “Monsters Inc.”, and “Finding Nemo”, I made paintings that reintroduce some of these famous characters. 
Releasing today June 5 in Japan. Global release coming soon…

The BABY MILO® BY *A BATHING APE® METAL FIGURINE is limited to 500 editions worldwide and encapsulates the essence of BAPE®'s beloved character, BABY MILO®, in a sleek and modern design. Crafted from 100% metal zinc alloy, this figurine exudes durability and quality. With a weight of 6.2KG and dimensions of 14.3cm X 24.5cm, it stands as a substantial piece that commands attention. The attention to detail is evident in every aspect of the figurine, from its intricate features to the meticulous craftsmanship. It serves as a testament to BAPE®'s commitment to excellence and innovation.

The BABY MILO® BY *A BATHING APE® METAL FIGURINE will be available at BAPE STORE® and US.BAPE.COM on Saturday, November 25th.

Thank you @bape_japan @bape_us @cherrychengyy
